!!<*yamlover:$defs:task>
Add the agile board renderer
description: Render a directory of tasks as kanban lanes with drag-to-retag.
priority: normal
assignee: claude
estimate: 1d
- Lanes come from the board's `workflow:` states; cards are the task members.
- A drag DELETEs the old state annotation and POSTs the new one — reusing `/api/annotate`.
